{"tid":1220076,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"作為一個基督徒 想表達幾句","createTime":"2019-06-14T02:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T03:06:15.000Z","uid":208536,"like":99,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6a31a2d52fbd0f319b3df838e4718a0c96a52188","tid":1220076,"uid":208536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:36:01.000Z","msg":"上連登幾年 由CD-ROM 到開ac<br />\n依幾日見證住連登風向由反耶<br />\n去到讚賞 支持<br />\n多謝大家<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">以下只代表個人感受 不代表教會或其他基督徒立場</span></span><br />\n<br />\n相信依幾日大家都見好多基督徒日以繼夜 夜以繼日咁係現場唱詩歌<br />\n而目的並唔係為左對抗<br />\n亦唔係要成為咩人民英雄<br />\n<br />\n只係因為我地相信既係神既公義會彰顯<br />\n當見到現場既流血衝突<br />\n警察對住手無寸鐵既市民使用過份武力<br />\n更加更加希望真係企出黎<br />\n用祈禱 唱聖詩 希望神會作工<br />\n<br />\n但依兩日 見到大家討論到<br />\n帶聖經 十字架<br />\n甚至建議基督徒行頭<br />\n<br />\n若果真係有心去接觸基督教<br />\n當然大家係樂見<br />\n但若果只係為左以基督徒作擋箭牌（只係若果）<br />\n未免有些少強人所難<br />\n對於我黎講<br />\n我係十分 超級 極度 唔願意見到<br />\n當我地願意有自己立場 而唔係依附政權<br />\n勇敢行出黎面對既時候<br />\n又再一次成為政治工具（別無映射）<br />\n<br />\n希望大家諒解<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">以上只代表個人感受 不代表教會或其他基督徒立場</span></span>"},{"pid":"109cfc7fedc7be83719307dcd029dbd168662365","tid":1220076,"uid":55571,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:37:57.000Z","msg":"其實我成間屋都無十字架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ef99501d655464dcc58a076543cb3e1878d268","tid":1220076,"uid":208536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"109cfc7fedc7be83719307dcd029dbd168662365","tid":1220076,"uid":55571,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:37:57.000Z","msg":"其實我成間屋都無十字架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:39:06.000Z","msg":"我都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聖經就好多本"},{"pid":"ace5e6fe6506c98aedd43e5ec59184481bcfcb43","tid":1220076,"uid":38321,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:40:24.000Z","msg":"支持！！<br />\n有心就跟基督徒一齊唱已經足夠<br />\n一定唔可以攞聖經 十字架黎玩<br />\n會好反感"},{"pid":"6711dd8070eaaa4d46af056664f3879782f09e33","tid":1220076,"uid":55571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32ef99501d655464dcc58a076543cb3e1878d268","tid":1220076,"uid":208536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"109cfc7fedc7be83719307dcd029dbd168662365","tid":1220076,"uid":55571,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:37:57.000Z","msg":"其實我成間屋都無十字架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:39:06.000Z","msg":"我都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聖經就好多本"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:40:54.000Z","msg":"我其實得靈修版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f631217cbd8d30c976e7742ccd3f29c5315f87e8","tid":1220076,"uid":83019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:41:34.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"9d3851f5a0caf1fb2b13d6cca063a27366b4465b","tid":1220076,"uid":55571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ace5e6fe6506c98aedd43e5ec59184481bcfcb43","tid":1220076,"uid":38321,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:40:24.000Z","msg":"支持！！<br />\n有心就跟基督徒一齊唱已經足夠<br />\n一定唔可以攞聖經 十字架黎玩<br />\n會好反感"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:42:36.000Z","msg":"其實<br />\n十字架只係個刑具<br />\n我無乜感覺<br />\n聖經就...差d"},{"pid":"dc3eb9daa4f29324187b2846fc0b2e55b0df8de4","tid":1220076,"uid":160405,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:43:07.000Z","msg":"太多人冇真係了解過宗教 但唔緊要 咪講多幾次 慢慢令佢地知道多啲囉"},{"pid":"67955b895a87673d71de812d95933269e4ffa93d","tid":122